Preheat grill. In a small bowl, combine pesto and tomato. Rub steaks with olive oil. Sprinkle with steak seasoning. Grill 6 to 8 minutes over high heat for medium rare or to desired degree of doneness. Remove to serving plate and cover loosely with foil. Let rest 5 minutes. Top steaks with tomato-pesto relish. Garnish with Parmesan cheese, optional.